title: About
text:
Harriet Sands newsletter creator
NHS Quarto Theme: Craig Robert Shenton, PhD author, maintainer.

A note on the Quarto theme this was built with:
It’s possible to create beautiful documentation to share online with Quarto that auto-updates with GitHub Actions.
This is an example of a Quarto website with an NHS Theme — it is a really powerful way to create and share your work. You can communicate about your work using the same reproducible workflow you and your colleagues use for analyses.
Quarto.org is the go-to place for full documentation and more tutorials For general guidance on how to use Quarto, please refer to the Quarto Tutorial site, and check out the R-Studio guide.
